<p>There are many alternatives, for example:</p>

<ul>
<li><p><strong>Alternative 1:</strong></p>

<pre><code>git fetch &amp;&amp; git checkout test
</code></pre>

<blockquote>
  <p>It's the most simple way.</p>
</blockquote></li>
<li><p><strong>Alternative 2:</strong></p>

<pre><code>git fetch
git checkout test
</code></pre>

<blockquote>
  <p>It's the same but in two steeps.</p>
</blockquote></li>
</ul>
